when updating the fmt submodule, the `libfmt.a` has to be rebuilt:
$ cd fmt
$ git clean -ffdx
$ mkdir build
$ cd build
$ cmake -DCMAKE_POSITION_INDEPENDENT_CODE:BOOL=true ..
$ make -j 8

build standalone binary:
$ make clean all

build python module
$ rm -rf build install
$ python3 setup.py install --install-lib install/
